[assistant] 抽取并记录信息: {"user_identity": "", "user_preference": "", "research_direction": "Neck disorders, including mechanical neck disorders (MND), whiplash associated disorders (WAD), myofascial neck pain, degenerative changes (osteoarthritis and cervical spondylosis), cervicogenic headache, and neck disorders with radicular findings", "filter_requirements": "Inclusion criteria: published or unpublished randomized controlled trials (RCTs) in any language. Exclusion criteria: quasi‐RCTs, clinical controlled trials (CCTs), studies investigating long tract signs (e.g., myelopathies), headache not of cervical origin, co‐existing headache without neck pain dominance or provocation, 'mixed' headaches, studies excluding manual therapy techniques, and studies using exercise plus another intervention versus the same intervention. Comparison groups: sham or placebo, no treatment or wait list, exercise plus another intervention vs that same intervention.", "rejection_reasons": "", "other_info": "Inclusion criteria include pain, measures of function/disability (e.g., neck disability index, activities of daily living), patient satisfaction, and global perceived effect/quality of life. Follow‐up duration: immediately post treatment (≤ one day), short‐term follow‐up (one day to three months), intermediate‐term follow‐up (three months up to, but not including, one year), and long‐term follow‐up (one year or longer). Extraction of adverse events and costs of care when available."}
